Soul may be observed.  
Soul may be experienced.  
Soul may influence everything.  

But until understanding matches scale,  
UNITAS refuses to pretend it can carry it.

Honesty is the guardrail.  
Simplicity is sacred.  

Soul≠counsuesness 


